Price Reduced Conveniently Located Close to Downtown 625 ad date: 10/14/2015 
Close to Downtown 625 Second Street, Crescent City, CA Great ocean view from apartment! Perfect live/work unit has a 1020 sq. ft. 2 bdrm & two half bath apartment upstairs w/separate gated entry and office, studio, professional space downstairs w/separate bath & laminate floor. Walking distance to city services, Beachfront Park, & businesses. Crescent City recognizes this as a 2 unit building. New windows in 2005, updated electrical with separate meters. No. 1400078 $249,000 Melissa Blackburn, Agent 1000 Northcrest Dr., Crescent City 707-954-3505 or 464-9741, #01073103
